cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.DC 

This paper deals with the virtualization and optimization of a multi-cell WLAN, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization problems and algorithms, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the implementation of the enhanced distributed channel access (EDCA) protocol, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and distributed computing (cs.DC).
